  <brief_title>Registry to Evaluate the ROX COUPLER in Patients With Resistant or Uncontrolled Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>ROX CONTROL HTN Registry: To Evaluate the ROX Coupler in Patients With Resistant or Uncontrolled Hypertension</official_title>
